{
  "stem": "2522.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a secondary and a tertiary because my father had all of these lieutenants, but they were dispersed in the villages, in the circumference of 25 kilometers of Trencin.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, absolutely familiar-- absolutely familiar, and including survival techniques.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, what mushrooms you eat and how you can dig up, for instance, dandelion and eat the roots.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hashomer Hatzair, the survival techniques, you know, what you can eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, you can scrounge fairly good food just if you know what you do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I went into the river, which bypassed all the checkpoints, swam couple, couple of kilometers, naked with my pants wrapped around my head, you know, with a belt.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was out of the way of Trencin, I just got out of the river and started walking in the direction of a mountain called Inovec.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Inovec is the tallest mountain in the-- in the Trencin district.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew the mountain very well, all the trails, and started moving in that direction because that's where the shooting, off and on, could be heard by distance.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to the cottage of a forester who my people-- my parents knew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Got some food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, the forester didn't want to keep me in the house, but at least it was a base from which to get food and get news about things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so during the night I came in and slept in a hayrick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And during the day, I was wandering through the mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On the second day of wandering around, I came across a small squad of Slovak soldiers who were on their way to, to, to the partisans, to join the partisans.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I came upon them and said, you know, I would like to join the partisans.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
